{"logo":"https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=8&quality=60&sec=1534502729&di=401173034db2f9628e397c02e4b9da7e&src=http%3A%2F%2Ff.hiphotos.baidu.com%2Fxiaodu%2Fpic%2Fitem%2Fa71ea8d3fd1f41349a83af522d1f95cad1c85e61.jpg","summary":"河南质量工程职业学院是一所以培养技术监督、质量检测类高级应用型人才为主的公办高等职业院校。学院位于河南省平顶山市，是河南省骨干高等职业院校、河南省职业教育品牌示范院校、河南省全民技能振兴工程高技能人才培养示范基地和全国中小学质量教育社会实践基地。学校前身是平顶山电大，始建于1980年。1996年，在平顶山电大的基础上，经河南省人民政府批准兴建了河南质量工程学校。2003年，以“电大”和河南省质量工程学校为依托升格为河南质量工程职业学院。截至2016年4月，学校占地58.5万㎡，建筑面积27.7万㎡。设7个系部，开设44个专业。学校教职工850人，有普通类全日制在校生和成人类在校生各6000多人。建有90个实验实训室，拥有图书资料58.59万册、电子图书2023.00G。","tags":["理工类","专科","公办"],"attrs":{"创建时间":"2003","所在地区":"河南省平顶山市高阳路中段","院校隶属":"河南省"},"imgs":["https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502729&di=e6b28816efff37cf5aa6f8b49048b6a2&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3630388660%2C885521720%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502729&di=f8488ad5d762fe380cd0c29423c801f3&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3575445594%2C3728361478%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502729&di=d3533310bb4b76803a794f660eff0c22&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3551746725%2C4030637326%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502729&di=f7df40cf6cb90f117f6d15c34c147adc&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft12.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3694359917%2C982944450%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pMbfm9GUKT-w/timg?wisealaddin&size=f300_300&quality=60&sec=1534502729&di=25058e8bbd241bbe05e287b3e5610ac2&src=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D3651310656%2C1001060967%26fm%3D179%26w%3D300%26h%3D300%26img.JPEG","https://ss0.bdstatic.com/9bA1vGfa2gU2pM